  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00939', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一種情況，最可能被視為違反社會工作倫理？', '["兒少機構社工師收受兒童自製的一張賀年卡", "老人機構社工師收受長輩自種的一把蔬菜", "醫院社工師收受案家的一個感謝紅包", "身障機構社工師收受小作所學員自製的一塊餅乾"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00940', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Reamer認為有效解決倫理難題的倫理決策架構，不包括下列何者？', '["指出受影響的人", "指出可採取的行動", "檢查每一個行動的利與弊", "舉辦公聽會"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00941', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '對助人工作者而言，會談是一種特殊的談話方式並具有其特性，個案工作者都會透過會談過程協助案主 解決問題或滿足需求，下列那一項不是會談的特性？', '["目的性", "角色性", "互惠性", "結構性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00942', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '任務中心模式是社會個案工作重要理論之一，有關該模式的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["該模式的重要貢獻在於將關注焦點從問題解決技巧轉移到個人治療取向", "不具有時限性的工作模式", "工作流程：預估、執行、結束／評估、若發現狀況未改善，需進行再次預估", "該模式是以專家中心而非以案主為中心的工作模式"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00943', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會個案工作者蒐集資料的目的，是為了對案主的問題或需求進行預估（assessment），預估的內涵通常 視案主的個別差異而有所不同，下列那一項不是在實務面經常進行的預估面向？', '["案主系統", "家庭系統", "政治系統", "生態系統"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00944', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '案主從學校畢業，正在找工作，接到面試通知，他說：「我恐怕這次的面試又不會成功，像前幾次一樣 又沒希望了。」下列社會個案工作者同理心的反應，何者層次最高？', '["由於過去失敗的經驗，你擔心這次也會失敗，好像不太有信心的樣子", "不會的，你要有信心，就會成功", "對於一個剛出校門的人，第一次找工作本來就比較困難，就是失敗了，也不算什麼", "你為何不去找那些面試成功的同學談，也許你就知道一些竅門了"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
